{"tid":1987232,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【區諾軒判刑】區軒：我不相信法治","createTime":"2020-04-24T10:37:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T12:38:50.000Z","uid":270576,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d3691bbed5c071d457e2e9a6fbf9c6aefd2db4f8","tid":1987232,"uid":270576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T10:37:54.000Z","msg":"法庭早前裁定區諾軒兩項襲警罪成，今（24日）判140小時社會服務令。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkft.tk/aunokhin\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkft.tk%2Faunokhin&d=6Js6kSUmrxq5WnxEZabkn4uQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=9f68213a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkft.tk/aunokhin</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ztkhZ1Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FztkhZ1Y.png&h=04f4568c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">他在審訴中一直保持緘默，<span style=\"color: red;\">「你問我，經歷了幾宗案件，我不會相信法治。</span>因為如果是『法治』，疑點歸於被告。刑事定罪高門檻的，一定被證明毫無合理疑點，才會被裁定有罪。如果說我有意圖去襲擊警員，哪我有什麼意圖去襲擊他（警員）？裁判官在判詞寫『明知』跟前面警員理論是沒有用的，那就像『讀心』一樣，可以假設議員在中間作溝通時會『明知』這是無用，你還會信法治嗎，我就不會再相信法治了」。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>Over my dead body</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望上訴成功推翻案例啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17a3a1b0d37b26179ab2102f191c2859c14d51d7","tid":1987232,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T10:39:37.000Z","msg":"區域法院做唔到案例㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"903b52686a6ba42d95f708df0c42e11402fdfcc6","tid":1987232,"uid":270576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17a3a1b0d37b26179ab2102f191c2859c14d51d7","tid":1987232,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T10:39:37.000Z","msg":"區域法院做唔到案例㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T10:40:11.000Z","msg":"頂 係咩 7左"},{"pid":"537326d8145038d30d6080811c36d6b7594b476f","tid":1987232,"uid":270576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T10:40:41.000Z","msg":"四月十八日，警方高調拘捕十五名民主派人士，指控其在去年八月及十月參與未經批准遊行，其中一人是區諾軒。他同日保釋候審，兩天後堅持按原訂的訪問日期受訪。「約了就要做。其實（狀態）是不會OK的，都幾痛苦。」<br />\n<br />\n堅持，是區諾軒對政治的態度，也是他從政十年所建立的形象。三次被捕，兩項襲警罪成，四月廿四日被判接受一百四十小時社會服務令。<br />\n<br />\n「大限」將至，他沒有停步，繼續推動民主派選舉協調。<br />\n<br />\n「無庸置疑，你問我個人，現時的狀態的確超越了我可以承受的境地。但邱吉爾說了一句說話：『堅持下去，並不是我們真的足夠堅強，而是我們別無選擇。』你放棄就甚麼都沒有了。」區軒說。"},{"pid":"3c8fccaffac89699107161f3305d859195dc8c9b","tid":1987232,"uid":137096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"17a3a1b0d37b26179ab2102f191c2859c14d51d7","tid":1987232,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T10:39:37.000Z","msg":"區域法院做唔到案例㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T10:41:29.000Z","msg":"同級法院可以拎黎做案例<br />\n高級法院就唔得"},{"pid":"a287b103fb883069ab7298b5046a2722ff63531e","tid":1987232,"uid":271513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T10:42:11.000Z","msg":"咁上唔上訴？"},{"pid":"a06e35e32f46bf28c3a4ad2295d7b0f9d1cdb883","tid":1987232,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a287b103fb883069ab7298b5046a2722ff63531e","tid":1987232,"uid":271513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T10:42:11.000Z","msg":"咁上唔上訴？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T10:47:34.000Z","msg":"上訴"},{"pid":"2190399137e0eb97ce6825c03b382cf507fcdbd1","tid":1987232,"uid":30476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a287b103fb883069ab7298b5046a2722ff63531e","tid":1987232,"uid":271513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T10:42:11.000Z","msg":"咁上唔上訴？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T10:59:26.000Z","msg":"佢咁樣判可能就係唔想你上訴"},{"pid":"4a89911723b3e1fa75817f57f0f494cc41b3b479","tid":1987232,"uid":51621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,